=========================================
UPDATES IDGET
=========================================

The Updates widget has 5 Variables
Three local and two global
Local Variables - News, enable javascript, Number of news items to
		 be displayed if js enabled
Global Variables - Enable of diable news, Enable javascript global

News variable - Two news items must be separated by a pipeline ' | '
		If a news item must point to a link, then specify 
		it at the end of the news item between [ ].
		For example News [link] | News2 [link2]
Numbeor of items- This is the number of items that has to be displayed
		 at a time i the ticker if javascript is enabled. 

To style the container of the news, specify it to the div 
#news_container
To style the news items, specify it to the #news ul and li. 		
